STEP fetch
  TAKES: url: str
  GIVES: summary: str
  MODE:  judgment

FLOW enrich
  TAKES: url: str
  GIVES: summary: str
  fetch(url=url)

FLOW batch
  TAKES: urls: List<str>
  GIVES: results: List<str>
  FOR EACH u IN urls PARALLEL AS results:
    enrich(url=u)

RESOURCES
  target: claude-workflow
  models: [haiku]
